description:
Get ready for Thrilling Party Pack,
a new downloadable content pack for Party Party Time!
Enjoy 10 brand new minigames!
Let's make the party even more exciting for everyone!

The Thrilling Party Pack includes the following content:

10 New Minigames:
6 Competitive Games
- Buoyant Battle
- Swing 'n' Jump
- Robot Race
- Jetpack Flight
- Block Walls
- Coin Slide
4 Co-op Games
- Wash It Clean!
- Point Ball
- Perfect Gears
- Maze Together
name: Thrilling Party Pack
